{"tid":1505222,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"去機場，唔好再唸啦，政府春袋必須要重擊！！","createTime":"2019-08-25T13:15:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T05:12:39.000Z","uid":232369,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"0acdb5757f4447c2dfb72cd0064ba0fec2e4b2d2","tid":1505222,"uid":232369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:15:31.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，今晚825嘅代價實在太重。我唔多講。<br />\n而家黑警重要冇啦啦開真槍！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">證明對家開始用最大武力去鎮壓我地，唔會有底線</span></span><br />\n竟然係咁，我覺得不如直接去機場啦。<br />\n黑警班仆街係味都開槍，射催淚彈，<br />\n咁不如索性攬炒啦屌！由佢地去機場放Tear gas!!!!<br />\n我受夠啦，我睇住勇武巴打被打被捉，真係好絕望<br />\n竟然係咁，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">機場攬炒啦</span>，我已經唔介意死了。<br />\n<br />\n有錯請屌，大家討論。"},{"pid":"e0b3207bba1f25acb35d399aa68b4d8e5930e838","tid":1505222,"uid":211412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:17:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e96d3bba732c2ad6b0e09ec03307d591d9b15220","tid":1505222,"uid":232369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:17:14.000Z","msg":"而家係最黑暗嘅時期啦！<br />\n會一直持續到10月1日<br />\n有成一個幾月啊屌<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地嘅手足已經唔夠啦</span>"},{"pid":"b150d289342f9b07e0aec56d4a3d8cdbfa3ed01d","tid":1505222,"uid":306917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:17:46.000Z","msg":"只有鬼先會反對去機場！"},{"pid":"85a00dfe2ef6b794574dd04691dc42955a2e8fa3","tid":1505222,"uid":232369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:19:03.000Z","msg":"竟然催淚彈有cyanide<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">攬炒啦屌</span>"},{"pid":"928f008fb2c794beaa083377b06fc74e4aba095a","tid":1505222,"uid":53592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:19:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90e675333ff41b0d9832ff6e7086ad934e5e152e","tid":1505222,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike